extends layouts/default
block variables
  -var bodyClass = 'service-template-default';
block content
  .inner-page.agencies-page
    <video autoplay muted loop class="bgVideo dec-video">
      <source src="images/bg_video_banner.mp4" type="video/mp4">
    </video>
      section.agencies__hero
        .container
          .agencies__title.aos-init(data-aos="fade-up"
            data-aos-duration="1000")
            h1 Surrogacy Agencies

          .agencies__title-content(data-aos="fade-up"
            data-aos-duration="1000")
            p Mitera’s Maternal-Fetal Medicine doctors are ready to help you prepare for a pregnancy journey. Whether a mom-to-be or a gestational carrier, our board-certified physicians are ready to assess your pregnancy risk and provide their expert guidance for the best possible pregnancy outcomes.
            p Mitera has the only standardized screening and certification program for surrogacy agencies that providesboth initial obstetrical screening and medical oversight during the entire journey to mitigate risk and optimize pregnancy outcomes.
      section.image-content
        .bg-decorator._bg-pink
          .container 
            .image-content__row(
              data-aos="fade-up"
              data-aos-delay='300'
              data-aos-duration="1000") 
              .image-content__image
                .section-dna-decor._top
                img(src='images/agencies_1.jpg') 
              .image-content__text.section__content
                .section-dna-decor._top
                .decorator
                h2 Fertility Centers
                p Let us take pregnancy risk assessment off your plate! Mitera’s team of      board-certified
                  strong Maternal-Fetal Medicine physicians (MFM’s)
                  | are licensed across the country and ready to help ease the load on fertilitycenters. Our 
                  strong  MFM’s 
                  | will manage the records review process in lieu of a nurse practitioner or reproductive endocrinologist and create a detailed report customized to the needs of the fertility practice. *
      section.agencies-program(
        data-aos="fade-up"
        data-aos-delay='300'
        data-aos-duration="1000")
        .ellipse-decor   
        .container 
          .agencies-program__row 
            .agencies-program__title
              
              h3 Mitera’s Certification Program
            .agencies-program__content.section__content
              p A Mitera certified program was specifically designed for surrogacy agencies and fertility centers. The program was created to engage and recognize leaders in 3rd party reproduction who are committed toupholding the highest medical standards. Surrogacy agencies and fertility centers that are certified by Mitera are recognized as being in the top tier in 3rd party reproduction providers.

      section.services-centers 
        .bg-decorator._bg-blue._circle.section-with-dna-decor
          .section-dna-decor._top
          <video autoplay muted loop class="bgVideoPartner dec-video">
            <source src="images/video2.mp4" type="video/mp4">
            </video>
          .container 
            .services-centers__content.section__content(
              data-aos="fade-up"
              data-aos-delay='300'
              data-aos-duration="1000"
            )
              h2 Why Get Mitera Certified?
              p A Mitera Maternal-Fetal Medicine (MFM) clearance is highly regarded in 3rd party reproduction. A MFMclearance eases the concerns of a fertility physician and is often considered a “green light” for a surrogatecandidate to proceed with fertility treatment.
              p 
                strong Suggested Appointment Types:
              ul 
                li Ensures a thorough pregnancy risk assessment.
                li Mitigates risk and optimizes outcomes during pregnancy
                li Streamlines clinic pre-approval.
                li Prevents delays in a surrogacy journey.
                li Empowers both gestational carriers and intended parents.
                li Provide medicolegal protection for agencies.
      section.guidance-sec.section-with-dna-decor.circle.circle_orange(id="certification")
        .bg-decorator.large._bg-orange._circle
          .container
            .guidance-sec__content.aos-init.surrogacy
              .section-title.aos-init(
                data-aos="fade-up"
                data-aos-duration="1000") Mitera Certification <br> Program
              .editor(
                data-aos="fade-up"
                data-aos-delay="200"
                data-aos-duration="1000")
                p Surrogacy agencies and fertility centers that are certified have a formal relationship with Mitera that commits their organizations to:
                ul
                  li
                    span
                      img(src='images/surr_img_1.svg' alt loading='lazy')
                    p Pre-match MFM screening of all surrogates
                  li
                    span
                      img(src='images/surr_img_2.svg' alt loading='lazy')
                    p Compliance with our recommendations
                  li
                    span
                      img(src='images/surr_img_3.svg' alt loading='lazy')
                    p Ongoing risk assessment and engagement during pregnancy
                p Our certified partners also have access to additional services such as MFM consultations for intended parents and at-home genetic testing and counseling
              .surrogacy__heading
                .section-title.aos-init(
                  data-aos="fade-up"
                  data-aos-duration="1000") Mitera Certification <br> Program
                .surrogacy__heading_video(
                  data-aos="fade-up"
                  data-aos-duration="1000")
                  img(src="images/pre_video.jpg" alt loading='lazy')
                  video(id = "my-video" src="images/video.mp4" controls preload="auto" muted)
      .container
        section.certified(
          id="agencies"
          data-aos="fade-up"
          data-aos-duration="1000")
          .certified__content
            .certified__content_description
              p
                strong Are you Mitera certified yet?
              p Partner with Mitera to provide peace of mind for your clients and ensure better outcomes for your organization.
            .certified__content_cta
              p Click here to schedule a call with a Mitera representative to learn more
              a(href='#').btn
                .btn__bg
                span Schedule
          .certified__bottom
            a(href='#').btn.surr_btn
              .btn__bg
              span.desk Click here to start the certification process
                <svg class="svg">
                <use xlink:href="images/sprite.svg#ic_arrow_right">
                </use>
                </svg>
              span.mob Start the certification process
                <svg class="svg">
                <use xlink:href="images/sprite.svg#ic_arrow_right">
                </use>
                </svg>


              
      
      section.services-text(
        data-aos="fade-up"
        data-aos-delay='300'
        data-aos-duration="1000"
            )
        .bg-decorator._bg-pink
          .container
            .services-text__content.section__content
              p *Mitera facilitators are not my facilitators of obstetric or genetic counseling care but rather facilitate an additional, independent third-party second opinion on risk stratification and/or assessment related to pregnancy (“Mitera Services”). The Mitera Services are considered "peer-to-peer" for the purposes of providing advice to my referring organization. No professional/patient relationship is created by using the information provided by or through the use of the Mitera Services. I understand that the Mitera facilitator will not prescribe medications for me and/or is not able to assist me in an emergency. If I require emergency care, I should call 911 or proceed to the nearest hospital emergency room for help.

